hopobject.body: Have you got any qualifications? caverta online uk Also, you clearly have no understanding of what bisexual means. Bisexual does not mean that one simultaneously has a relationship with a male and a female. All bisexual means is that one is attracted to both sexes. A person who is bisexual who was married to one person and sleeping with another would be committing infidelity as much as a straight person who was married to one person and sleeping with another.
